<div class="aos-W100"><a data-fancybox="gallery" data-caption="Photo of 2017 Winner" href="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/328/patrice.jpg"><img src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/DAM/328/patrice.jpg" loading="lazy" class="aos-W100 aos-DB aos-MBS" alt="Photo of 2017 Winner" title="Photo of 2017 Winner"></a></div>
